&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree (or 4 additional years of relevant experience)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8 years of experience designing and implementing AI/ML governance frameworks for enterprise-scale environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated expertise with responsible AI practices, model risk management, and regulatory compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must meet DoD 8140 requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
